vote.title: Authorize an amendment to Ordinance No. 26147, previously approved on October 26, 2005 to modify the composition of the board of directors for Tax Increment Financing Reinvestment Zone Number Thirteen (Grand Park South TIF District) in accordance with the Tax Increment Financing Act, as amended, V.T.C.A Texas Tax Code, Chapter 311 (the “Act”) - Financing: No cost consideration to the City
